OL,3,C'I wanna make memories': Boy appeals
OL,4,Cfor help to complete bucket list
OL,6,FITV Granada Reports correspondent
OL,7,FVictoria Grimes has been speaking to
OL,8,FAlfie Sales, who is trying to raise
OL,9,Fmoney to complete his bucket list.
OL,11,FA 11-year-old rugby fan who lives with
OL,12,Fa life-limiting condition is trying to
OL,13,Fraise "as much money as I can" so he
OL,14,Fcan "create memories" with his family
OL,15,Fwhile he is still able.
OL,17,FAlfie Sales, from Leigh, has Duchenne
OL,18,FMuscular Dystrophy, a rare genetic
OL,19,Fcondition that predominantly affects
OL,20,Fboys and causes all muscles in the
OL,21,Fbody to waste away over time.
