OL,3,C'I wanna make memories': Boy appeals
OL,4,Cfor help to complete bucket list
OL,6,FSince Alfie's diagnosis, his parents
OL,7,Flaunched the campaign Action4Alfie,
OL,8,Fwhich calls for research into the
OL,9,Fcondition and raises funds for
OL,10,Fanything the youngster may need as his
OL,11,Fcondition worsens.
OL,13,FThe young rugby and football fan is
OL,14,Fappealing to members of the rugby
OL,15,Fcommunity to donate signed rugby
OL,16,Fshirts that he can auction off - with
OL,17,Fall the money raised going towards
OL,18,Fliving out his wish list.
