OL,3,C'I wanna make memories': Boy appeals
OL,4,Cfor help to complete bucket list
OL,6,F"We're going to auction the shirts so
OL,7,Fwe can create memories with my
OL,8,Ffamily," Alfie said. "I'd like to
OL,9,Ftrain with Liverpool FC and go to
OL,10,Fwatch a football team abroad. I want
OL,11,Fto raise as much money as I can for my
OL,12,Fbucket list."
OL,14,FAlfie kicked off his campaign with a
OL,15,Fsocial media video which has been
OL,16,Fwidely viewed and featured on Granada
OL,17,FReports
OL,19,FWhat is Duchenne Muscular Dystrophy?
