OL,3,C'I wanna make memories': Boy appeals
OL,4,Cfor help to complete bucket list
OL,6,FOn Wednesday, 6 August, Alfie visited
OL,7,Fthe Leigh Leopards stadium and was
OL,8,Fsurprised by his rugby heroes - who
OL,9,Fall signed memorabilia for him to be
OL,10,Fsold at a special auction organised by
OL,11,FSuper League Raw Weekly podcast.
OL,13,FThe 11 year-old is a lifelong fourth
OL,14,Fgeneration fan of the club. His dad
OL,15,FKieron and grandad were both invited
OL,16,Falong with him.
OL,18,FAlfie's sister Mila Rose and cousin
OL,19,FFinlay were both on hand to help get
OL,20,Fshirts and rugby balls signed for him.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
