OL,3,C'I wanna make memories': Boy appeals
OL,4,Cfor help to complete bucket list
OL,6,FAlfie's dad, Kieron Sales, said: "The
OL,7,Fresponse has already been incredible.
OL,8,FThe shirts have been coming in from
OL,9,Fall directions which is amazing -
OL,10,Fwe're so overwhelmed.
OL,12,F"Alfie is not defined by his
OL,13,Fcondition. We're trying to instil in
OL,14,Fhim to take the positives and that's
OL,15,Fwhat this is all about.
OL,17,F"When he was diagnosed it was a really
OL,18,Ftough time so we set up Action4Alfie,
OL,19,Fnot just fundraising for Alfie but for
OL,20,Fthe charities who have supported him.
OL,21,FHe is so inspirational."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
