OL,3,C'I wanna make memories': Boy appeals
OL,4,Cfor help to complete bucket list
OL,6,FOwner of Leigh Leopards, Derek
OL,7,FBeaumont, said: "Alfie is great. It's
OL,8,Fa great initiative and I'm so glad we
OL,9,Fcan support it. He has got a real
OL,10,Flevel of importance, something he is
OL,11,Fowning and achieving.
OL,13,F"Unfortunately, a lot of people that
OL,14,Fhave struggles in life don't get to do
OL,15,Fthat. To champion him and try to make
OL,16,Fthings as normal as possible for him,
OL,17,Fit's something we're really keen on."
