OL,6,FAlfie first appeared on Granada
OL,7,FReports aged six during lockdown in
OL,8,F2020. His Toy Story themed birthday
OL,9,Fparty had to be cancelled because he
OL,10,Fhad to isolate during the Pandemic.
OL,12,FThe auction is due to take place in
OL,13,FNovember 2025.
